OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA bright end
OL,6,Fto the afternoon with a few blustery
OL,7,Fshowers lingering into the evening,
OL,8,Fhowever most places becoming dry
OL,9,Fovernight with cloudier skies
OL,10,Fdeveloping in the south. A chillier
OL,11,Fnight ahead with winds easing and a
OL,12,Ftouch of frost.
OL,13,
OL,14,CFriday:FA dry start, but cloudy skies
OL,15,Falready across the south of the region
OL,16,Fwill continue to spread north with
OL,17,Foutbreaks of rain arriving during the
OL,18,Fevening. Becoming rather breezy later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
