OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:
OL,6,FUnsettled through the weekend and
OL,7,FMonday with sunny spells and showers
OL,8,For longer spells of rain. The showers
OL,9,Flocally heavy with thunder. Windy with
OL,10,Fcoastal gales possible, temperatures
OL,11,Fnear average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
